    "description": "Grow your career with Ashok Leyland! We are hiring a Distribution Manager for our Indore team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Ashok Leyland:\nAshok Leyland is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Referral bonus program\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ashok Leyland!",
